<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    
    <!-- Google Fonts: Nunito (Rounded) & Inter (Clean) -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Nunito:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Fira+Code:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Remix Icon (Modern Icons) -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Animate.css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    
    <!-- Highlight.js -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.9.0/styles/atom-one-dark.min.css">
    
    <!-- Material Design Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/material.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="md-container">
        <!-- Material App Bar -->
        <header class="md-app-bar animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
            <div class="md-app-bar-content">
                <div class="md-app-bar-title">
                    <div class="md-app-bar-logo">
                        <i class="ri-markdown-fill"></i>
                        <span>MD Editor</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md-app-bar-subtitle">Pro</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="md-app-bar-actions">
                    <!-- Render Mode Chips -->
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-right: 16px;">
                        <div class="md-chip active" id="mdCustomChip">
                            <i class="ri-palette-line"></i>
                            Custom
                        </div>
                        <div class="md-chip" id="mdBasicChip">
                            <i class="ri-text"></i>
                            Basic
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Theme Toggle -->
                    <button class="md-btn md-btn-icon" id="mdThemeToggle" title="Toggle Theme">
                        <i class="ri-moon-line"></i>
                    </button>
                    
                    <!-- Action Buttons -->
                    <button class="md-btn md-btn-outlined" id="mdSave" title="Save (Ctrl+S)">
                        <i class="ri-save-3-line"></i>
                        <span>Save</span>
                    </button>
                    
                    <button class="md-btn md-btn-outlined" id="mdLoad" title="Load File">
                        <i class="ri-folder-open-line"></i>
                        <span>Load</span>
                    </button>
                    
                    <button class="md-btn md-btn-contained" id="mdExport" title="Export HTML (Ctrl+E)">
                        <i class="ri-download-cloud-2-line"></i>
                        <span>Export</span>
                    </button>
                    
                    <button class="md-btn md-btn-text" id="mdClear" title="Clear Editor">
                        <i class="ri-delete-bin-line"></i>
                        <span>Clear</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="md-main animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__delay-0.5s">
            <div class="md-editor-container">
                <!-- Editor Pane -->
                <div class="md-pane md-editor-pane">
                    <div class="md-pane-header">
                        <div class="md-pane-title">
                            <i class="ri-edit-circle-line"></i>
                            <span>Editor</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md-pane-stats">
                            <span id="mdCharCount">0 chars</span>
                            <span id="mdWordCount">0 words</span>
                            <span id="mdLineCount">0 lines</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Material Toolbar -->
                    <div class="md-toolbar">
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="bold" title="Bold (Ctrl+B)">
                            <i class="ri-bold"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="italic" title="Italic (Ctrl+I)">
                            <i class="ri-italic"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="strikethrough" title="Strikethrough">
                            <i class="ri-strikethrough"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="heading" title="Heading">
                            <i class="ri-h-1"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="md-shortcut-divider"></div>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="link" title="Link (Ctrl+K)">
                            <i class="ri-link"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="image" title="Image">
                            <i class="ri-image-line"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="code" title="Inline Code">
                            <i class="ri-code-line"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="codeblock" title="Code Block">
                            <i class="ri-code-box-line"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="quote" title="Quote">
                            <i class="ri-double-quotes-l"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="md-shortcut-divider"></div>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="list" title="Bullet List">
                            <i class="ri-list-unordered"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="numberedlist" title="Numbered List">
                            <i class="ri-list-ordered"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="checklist" title="Task List">
                            <i class="ri-checkbox-line"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="hr" title="Horizontal Rule">
                            <i class="ri-separator"></i>
                        </button>
                        <button class="md-shortcut-btn" data-action="table" title="Table">
                            <i class="ri-table-2"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="md-pane-content">
                        <textarea 
                            id="mdEditor" 
                            class="md-editor"
                            placeholder="Start typing your markdown here...

# Welcome to Material Editor

## Features
- **Material Design** interface
- **Clean aesthetics** with subtle animations
- **Modern typography** using Google Fonts
- **Two render modes**: Custom and Basic
- **Dark/Light theme** support
- **Keyboard shortcuts** for productivity

## Render Modes
- **Custom Mode**: Enhanced Material Design styling with beautiful typography and visual effects
- **Basic Mode**: Clean, minimal styling with beautiful fonts but standard appearance

## Shortcuts
- **Ctrl+S**: Save document
- **Ctrl+E**: Export to HTML
- **Ctrl+B**: Bold text
- **Ctrl+I**: Italic text
- **Ctrl+K**: Insert link
- **Ctrl+R**: Toggle render mode

## Code Example
```javascript
function hello() {
    console.log('Welcome to Material Design!');
}
```

> "Design is not just what it looks like and feels like. Design is how it works."

[Visit Material Design](https://material.io)

---

| Feature | Status |
|---------|--------|
| Editor | Active |
| Preview | Live |
| Export | Ready |

**Experience the beauty of Material Design!**"
                        ><%= initialContent %></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Material Divider -->
                <div class="md-divider" id="mdDivider"></div>

                <!-- Preview Pane -->
                <div class="md-pane md-preview-pane">
                    <div class="md-pane-header">
                        <div class="md-pane-title">
                            <i class="ri-eye-line"></i>
                            <span>Preview</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md-pane-stats">
                            <span id="renderMode">Custom Render</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="md-pane-content">
                        <div id="mdPreview" class="md-preview md-custom-render">
                            <!-- Preview content will be rendered here -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <!-- Hidden file input -->
    <input type="file" id="mdFileInput" accept=".md,.txt" style="display: none;">

    <!-- Material Design Application Script -->
    <script src="/js/material.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
